name: Wounding Blow
extFlavorText: Farmhands, villagers, and slaves - easily replaceable wretches that must be taught the joys of obedience.

name: Critical Strike
extFlavorText: There is no mercy on the battlefield; it's brothers against sisters, and blood against blood. For resentment breeds betrayal, as anger leads to rage, and fear to hate. This endless feud, from whence did it arise, and when will it see an end?

name: Brutal Assault
extFlavorText: "By the all-seeing eye, I spill this blood in your image, I sacrifice this foul beast unto you, that you might take- Wait. What are you doing? Don't- no!" - Septus
